# 🌍 FDF Three.js Terrain Visualizer

Welcome to the **FDF Three.js Terrain Visualizer**! This project is a powerful and interactive 3D wireframe visualizer built using [Three.js](https://threejs.org/). It allows users to create, customize, and explore 3D terrains using data inputs or predefined maps. With a focus on customization and ease of use, this tool is perfect for anyone interested in visualizing topographic data or experimenting with map generation.

## 🚀 Features

- **Interactive 3D Terrain Rendering**: Create and explore terrains in 3D with real-time controls.
- **Map Builder**: Input your custom terrain data directly through a simple interface.
- **Predefined Maps**: Quickly load and visualize several predefined maps including France, Mars, Pyramide, and 42.
- **Advanced Color Fading**: Customize the terrain colors with fading effects.
- **Responsive Design**: Works well on different screen sizes, with a clean and intuitive UI.

